kuberi tahu pada kalian.

11
00:01:19,640 --> 00:01:20,520
Apa?

12
00:01:23,360 --> 00:01:24,200
Itu...

13
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:27,800
Ini.

14
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:31,080
Apa ini?

15
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:33,320
Ini rahasia Li Xiaolian.

16
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:36,040
Putranya, Gu Chunsheng,

17
